<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="loyal-adj">loyal <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'lɔɪəl/    美 /'lɔɪəl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>忠诚的；忠实的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a loyal friend</strong>
忠实的朋友</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He has <strong>remained loyal to</strong> his political principles.
他坚持自己的政治原则。</p></div>

